Package com.quantum.utils.config

package com.quantum.utils.config
Provides utilities for configuration management and localization.

This package includes classes for handling configuration properties and localization through resource bundles. It offers functionality for loading, managing, and saving configuration properties, as well as providing localized messages based on language and country settings.

Classes

  • LanguageBundle - Provides access to localized messages from resource bundles. Allows retrieving localized strings based on the current locale and language settings.
  • ConfigurationProperties - Manages the configuration properties for the application. Supports loading, retrieving, setting, and saving properties from/to a properties file.
